#: ../../source/unit/bps.rst:2 dc1371241fab4c649935df2c54677fc6
msgid "BPS Unit"
msgstr "BPS 单位"

#: ../../source/unit/bps.rst:6 04db295ba5aa457f881ffc35287ce9f4
msgid ""
"The Barometric Pressure Sensor(BPS) ``BPS Unit`` is a barometer unit that"
" uses Bosch BMP280 pressure sensor(BPS) or QMP6988 barometric pressure "
"sensor(BPS V1.1) to measure atmospheric pressure, temperature and "
"altitude estimation."
msgstr ""
"气压传感器（BPS）``BPS Unit`` 是一款气压计单元，使用 Bosch BMP280 压力传感器（BPS）或 QMP6988 "
"气压传感器（BPS V1.1）来测量大气压力、温度并进行高度估算。"

